Bluedorn in April 2007 was named Chief Executive Officer, and was elected a director, of Lennox International Inc., a Richardson, Texas-based provider of climate control solutions for the heating, air conditioning and refrigeration markets. He was appointed Chairman of the Board in May 2012. A former military officer, Bluedor 
Personal Attributes and Interests

Bluedorn played basketball in high school.

