Todd M. Bluedorn 
Executive Compensation
As Chairman and Chief Executive Officer at LENNOX INTERNATIONAL INC, Todd M. Bluedorn  made $8,582,381 in total compensation.  Of this total $1,084,000 was received as a salary, $2,620,028 was received as a bonus, $954,887 was received in stock options, $3,876,723 was awarded as stock and $46,743 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


